Privacy Policy for Rami Tounsi

Effective date: April 15, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how Rami Tounsi ("the App", "we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, stores, and shares information when you use the mobile game Rami Tounsi.

By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

1. Who We Are

Rami Tounsi is a mobile card game that includes offline play, online competitive play, player profiles, rankings, badges, optional voice chat during matches, and cloud-based account recovery.

If you need to contact us regarding privacy or data protection matters, you can use the following contact details:

